  "detailed_description": "<h1>ALSO RECOMMENDED FOR YOU</h1><p></p><br><h1>GAMES FROM MY FRIENDS</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>Frisbee For FUN!</strong><br>Frisbee is joy, Frisbee is fun!<br>You are a very mischievous kitten that uses helpless chickens as targets.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The distance may vary;<br></li><li>Chickens will start to run;<br></li><li>Portals will appear;<br></li><li>The wind will drive you crazy!</li></ul><br>What to expect? Hit targets, but be careful ... being a bad kitten can have consequences.<br><br><strong>Freedom to the chickens!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1422880/extras/3a7c40c23a39b4b25c7954426a5e03f9.poster.avif?t=1620999312\" width=600 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1422880/extras/3a7c40c23a39b4b25c7954426a5e03f9.webm?t=1620999312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1422880/extras/3a7c40c23a39b4b25c7954426a5e03f9.mp4?t=1620999312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1422880/extras/e2b710ae4690b4774113417dbbde9d02.poster.avif?t=1620999312\" width=600 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1422880/extras/e2b710ae4690b4774113417dbbde9d02.webm?t=1620999312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1422880/extras/e2b710ae4690b4774113417dbbde9d02.mp4?t=1620999312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.co